<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>로그인</title>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>로그인</h1>
    <form action="/login" method="POST">
        <label for="id">아이디:</label>
        <input type="text" id="id" name="id" value="<%= rememberedId %>" required><br>
        <label for="pw">비밀번호:</label>
        <input type="password" id="pw" name="pw" required><br>
        <label>
            <!-- rememberedId : '아이디 기억하기' 체크박스를 체크했을때 쿠키에서 아이디를 가져옴 -> 아이디 있을때는 입력창에 아이디 대입  -->
            <input type="checkbox" name="remember" value="1" <%= rememberedId ? 'checked' : '' %>> 아이디 기억하기
        </label><br />
        <button type="submit">로그인</button>
    </form>
</body>
</html>